&lt;li&gt;Maintain documentation for data sources, metric logic, and reporting processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the business-side owner of Support data—partnering with engineering on data quality in Zendesk and Salesforce&lt;/li&gt;
