&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4–6 years in an analytics, reporting, or business analyst role supporting Customer Support, CX, or operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid SQL skills—ability to pull and manipulate data independently across multiple source systems&lt;/li&gt;
